			"Best for clients interested in NAD+ as part of a broader wellness, recovery, or performance routine who want a monitored setting and clear expectations.",
		cards: [
			{
				title: "Route matters",
				body:
					"Eden can discuss route, dose, and timing so clients understand what kind of visit they are booking.",
